{"tid":670066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國「天網」無所不在！ 中學課室也裝設人臉辨識...","createTime":"2018-05-19T04:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T15:38:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"67700007e8ab71b325a6972c3adf7ab0e3cde8b3","tid":670066,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php6bBjOm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php6bBjOm.jpg&h=dec50703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國在境內各大城市裝設「天網」監控系統，能夠以人臉辨識迅速尋獲當局要抓捕的罪犯，但也引起侵犯隱私的疑慮，如今連國中校園也遭人臉辨識監視器入侵，讓不少學生不寒而慄！<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，浙江杭州第十一中學部分教室內，近來裝設了結合3個攝影鏡頭的「天眼」，能夠捕捉學生臉部表情，打瞌睡或不專心一下子就能被分辨出來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpxCiu07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpxCiu07.jpg&h=82de3c73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該校副校長張冠超解釋，這其實是「智慧課堂行為分析系統」，對學生課堂的專注情況一目了然，若在系統上顯示為黃色，則代表他相當認真；若顯示為藍色，則說明學生可能心不在焉。<br />\n<br />\n張冠超說，最後得到的結果會提供給老師了解，好調整上課的模式，至於是否會侵犯到隱私？他澄清系統在收集訊息後會產生代碼，並利用這些代碼來展開運算，不會擷取學生的臉部照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php9Bo6gR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php9Bo6gR.jpg&h=6a60ccb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但21世紀教育研究院副院長熊丙奇認為，這種做法會讓小孩性格扭曲，培養出「表演型人格」，而且感到自己被當成犯人對待。<br />\n<br />\n杭州第十一中學的學生們受訪時，也坦言該系統應該沒有什麼幫助，也有人抱怨一直被監控很難受。不過副校長張冠超指出，下學期全校教室都會加裝「智慧課堂行為分析系統」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2430739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2430739&d=QhqAE%2BowGebsppo1Z3Gpx4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=944b7faf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2430739&h=7e40616c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2430739</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/79/84/a5/7984a56f72a06479f85f26949ba464ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F79%2F84%2Fa5%2F7984a56f72a06479f85f26949ba464ef.jpg&h=1d4962e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce21b0549da4e44443919b294fd64d8323b5fe61","tid":670066,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7feff1a824c49d6301e4d078f158b8a081ecf2","tid":670066,"uid":127991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"大陸好興搵人代上堂點名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e02e22edfa9912a9c1572c712de7c7fe3ffd23e","tid":670066,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"痴線"},{"pid":"a76120e5cfe0f9330613e2df5f8b9e306e836a70","tid":670066,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:19:26.000Z","msg":"幾時啲支那豬要打晶片？"},{"pid":"80023f059a73a4d4a8133581027b86581d65ce31","tid":670066,"uid":61271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"大陸人權是最好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121f2c73223d482c46f3452aeee1903c983ff1d3","tid":670066,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"幾咁唔信任市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbd86b0a26398931f8edfb69ae58fb508a6b19d","tid":670066,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:34:42.